{
  "texts": [
    "In their method, point cloud descriptors are obtained with PointNetVLAD (Uy and Lee 2018) and image-based descriptors are extracted using ResNet50.",
    "A fully-connected layer is then employed to produce a compact global multimodal descriptor for each place.",
    "Their network finally learns an optimal metric to describe the similarity of the fused global descriptors for end-to-end place recognition.",
    "Lu et al. (2020) proposed PIC-Net, a point cloud and image collaboration network for large-scale place recognition.",
    "PIC-Net uses spatial attention VLAD to fuse the discriminative points and pixels, and mines the complementary information between the image and point cloud."
  ]
}